{"tha-ap341:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap341:0.2":"Gandhodakavagga ","tha-ap341:0.3":"9 Dhammasavaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap341:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap341:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap341:1.3":"Catusaccam pakasento, ","tha-ap341:1.4":"santaresi bahum janam. ","tha-ap341:2.1":"Aham tena samayena, ","tha-ap341:2.2":"jatilo uggatapano; ","tha-ap341:2.3":"Dhunanto vakacirani, ","tha-ap341:2.4":"gacchami ambare tada. ","tha-ap341:3.1":"Buddhasetthassa upari, ","tha-ap341:3.2":"gantum na visahamaham; ","tha-ap341:3.3":"Pakkhiva selamasajja, ","tha-ap341:3.4":"gamanam na labhamaham. ","tha-ap341:4.1":"Na me idam bhutapubbam, ","tha-ap341:4.2":"iriyassa vikopanam; ","tha-ap341:4.3":"Dake yatha ummujjitva, ","tha-ap341:4.4":"evam gacchami ambare. ","tha-ap341:5.1":"Ularabhuto manujo, ","tha-ap341:5.2":"hetthasino bhavissati; ","tha-ap341:5.3":"Handa menam gavesissam, ","tha-ap341:5.4":"api attham labheyyaham. ","tha-ap341:6.1":"Orohanto antalikkha, ","tha-ap341:6.2":"saddamassosi satthuno; ","tha-ap341:6.3":"Aniccatam kathentassa, ","tha-ap341:6.4":"tamaham uggahim tada. ","tha-ap341:7.1":"Aniccasannamuggayha, ","tha-ap341:7.2":"agamasim mamassamam; ","tha-ap341:7.3":"Yavatayum vasitvana, ","tha-ap341:7.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap341:8.1":"Carime vattamanamhi, ","tha-ap341:8.2":"Tam dhammasavanam sarim; ","tha-ap341:8.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap341:8.4":"Tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap341:9.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap341:9.2":"devaloke ramim aham; ","tha-ap341:9.3":"Ekapannasakkhattunca, ","tha-ap341:9.4":"devarajjamakarayim. ","tha-ap341:10.1":"Ekasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap341:10.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap341:10.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap341:10.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap341:11.1":"Pitugehe nisiditva, ","tha-ap341:11.2":"samano bhavitindriyo; ","tha-ap341:11.3":"Gathaya paridipento, ","tha-ap341:11.4":"aniccatamudahari. ","tha-ap341:12.1":"Anussarami tam sannam, ","tha-ap341:12.2":"samsaranto bhavabhave; ","tha-ap341:12.3":"Na kotim pativijjhami, ","tha-ap341:12.4":"nibbanam accutam padam. ","tha-ap341:13.1":"Anicca vata sankhara, ","tha-ap341:13.2":"uppadavayadhammino; ","tha-ap341:13.3":"Uppajjitva nirujjhanti, ","tha-ap341:13.4":"tesam vupasamo sukho. ","tha-ap341:14.1":"Saha gatham sunitvana, ","tha-ap341:14.2":"pubbakammam anussarim; ","tha-ap341:14.3":"Ekasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap341:14.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap341:15.1":"Jatiya sattavassoham, ","tha-ap341:15.2":"arahattamapapunim; ","tha-ap341:15.3":"Upasampadayi buddho, ","tha-ap341:15.4":"gunamannaya cakkhuma. ","tha-ap341:16.1":"Darakova aham santo, ","tha-ap341:16.2":"karaniyam samapayim; ","tha-ap341:16.3":"Kim me karaniyam ajja, ","tha-ap341:16.4":"sakyaputtassa sasane. ","tha-ap341:17.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap341:17.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap341:17.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap341:17.4":"saddhammasavane phalam. ","tha-ap341:18.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap341:18.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap341:18.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap341:19.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dhammasavaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap341:20.1":"Dhammasavaniyattherassapadanam navamam. "}